data.description: Fully furnished home in Cresco with character, updates, and a large private yard. Open concept, cozy living area with wood-burning fireplace and hardwood floors THROUGHOUT. Main floor bedroom, full bathroom and laundry. Plus additional two bedrooms and full bathroom upstairs. Screened-in porch to enjoy which overlooks the large, private backyard, with grill included. One car built-in garage, and finished bonus room in the basement for additional entertainment space and storage. Includes all quality furniture, grill, games, and decor for a turn-key vacation or full-time home! Convenient location to Route 191 and 80, but quiet wooded neighborhood to enjoy. Short Term Rentals Possible! Current STR permit in place.
